HEADWORD: Cladonia
<hw>Cladonia</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the type genus of
<fam>Cladoniaceae</fam>; lichens characterized by a crustose thallus and
capitate fruiting bodies borne on simple or branched podetia.</def>⟦br⟧
